<taxonomicName box="[643,731,1261,1285]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Anoreina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nana">
<emphasis box="[643,731,1261,1285]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">A. nana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
the anterior margin of the pronotum has an interrupted row of coarse punctures.
</paragraph>
